Name: Zagan Must Be Rescued
About the game: Zagan Must Be Rescued is a FPS survival game where you will feel the fear and excitement in your marrow . you will have your weapon and teleport ability to fight against enemies that are turning around. Features: - Fight alone against enemies that increase in every wave from the start of the game. - Ammo is unlimited but use the features of your weapons according to your game style. - Set your own play style on each different map. -Break your record with the points you earn in every enemy you kill. -Determine your game tactics according to the increasing number of enemies in each wave
